    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The alternative, of course, is to plan ahead.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "To do your research. To anticipate the effects. To avoid the consequences of poor action by way of elimination or mitigation. To make things ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "better",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " for everyone involved—your stakeholders, your people, posterity too.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
